        @Since(value="7.0")
public CreateVolumeRequest(String name,
                         Long accountID,
                         Long totalSize,
                         Boolean enable512e,
                         Optional<QoS> qos,
                         Optional<Map<String,Object>> attributes)
        The Request object for the "CreateVolume" API Service call.
        Parameters:
        name - [required] Name of the volume.
        accountID - [required] AccountID for the owner of this volume.
        totalSize - [required] Total size of the volume, in bytes. Size is rounded up to the nearest 1MB size.
        enable512e - [required] Should the volume provides 512-byte sector emulation?
        qos - (optional) Initial quality of service settings for this volume.
        attributes - (optional) List of Name/Value pairs in JSON object format.
        Since:
        7.0
